		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was thinking about something mapper-independent.
<br />And I could only think about CHRRAM-SRAM.
<br />32KB SRAM + BATTERY would be nice with external switches on the cartridge to select the bank.
<br />No gui or boot, only a switch on the exterior.
<br />
<br />As in the Aladdin a Lockout defeat chip would be useful too.

		

